commit.message: Fixed some spelling error and fixed an alert to display correct info.

Added Tan's Java files, fixed congested logic, fixed congestion bug (cant be down then congested, if a station is down it cant change until its back up), added charts button on each cell to show graphs instead of clicking cell which will be easier for user, fixed other pesky bugs
Can now simulate what the refreshing of new data would look like, can detect if station is down, couple bugs to fix

Graph bug fixed, all graphs are done now (pie chart, line chart, bar chart) yah yeet, also changed status colors so they are better to see, added all the graphs to a stack view, added animations to graphs, increased font size on graphs so they are easier to read, thats all i can remember
Added new json files and python scripts

Another big push coming in watch out. Added icons to setting panel, added another settings options, added contact us functionality, imbeded Material Design API for pretty buttons :), added the congestion page where the user can pick a congestion threshold and all the functionality that comes with that (decent amount), added scroll view to graph page, graph are not done yet some are showing false data, added conjested feature willl it will turn yellow and update status if it is contested, thats all i can remember
